    					<br>Toilet Usage</br>
    					<br>Sink Usage</br>
 					 </br>
 					<p class="section-paragraph paragraph-size">By having this data, caregivers may begin to track patterns in activities, as well as taking note of any unsual/questionable data to make sure that the patient is being safe.</p>
